Carol Raye https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carol_Raye 0 Carol Raye (born 17 January 1923) also billed as Carole Raye, is a retired English-born actress of film, television and theatre, comedian, singer, dancer and radio and television producer and director. She started her career in the United Kngdom in theatre and television and starring film roles. After emigrating to Australia in 1962, she became best known for her television and there in serials and TV films, later returning to theatre roles after joining the Theatre Board of the Council of Australia.
